item.title: Easy but forgot how 2 do wear do i change home teleport
item.dc:creator: @sombohdi sombohdi
item.description:
@sombohdi wrote:

Alright, follow the steps.

1.) Find a square spot in edgeville you would like your home teleport to go too.
2.) Type ::mypos, and it will tell you the X and Y Coords.
3.) Go to your source and search for “clicking buttons”.
4.) In Clicking buttons, search for “Home Teleport” and change the coords to the one you got when you said ::mypos.
5.) Save and compile.

I hope this helped.
